{"tid":2013564,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"天津權健解散","createTime":"2020-05-12T11:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T12:06:50.000Z","uid":13106,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1f91ca9f289f567462792375f9df90355c9cda","tid":2013564,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:18:37.000Z","msg":"中超聯球會天津天海發出公告，表示財務狀況到了難以為繼的絕境，無力維持正常營運，球會正式宣告解散。<br />\n<br />\n天津天海的前身為天津權健，權健集團在2015年入主球會，2016年由意大利名宿簡拿華路出任主帥，贏得中甲冠軍升上中超，曾簽入多名球星，包括巴西前鋒柏圖、比利時中場韋素等，首季出戰中超就得到季軍。<br />\n<br />\n但在去年，權健董事長束昱輝涉嫌組織、領導傳銷活動等罪被捕，球會其後被天津足協託管，再改名為天津天海。內地傳媒報道，萬通控股有意收購球會，但在權責問題上未能達成共識，預料天津天海的中超席位會由深圳佳兆業補上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525674-20200512.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525674-20200512.htm&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=081d6da2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525674-20200512.htm&h=6f0e8911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525674-20200512.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3b12bfb1b8d8ec64317880c551fef8f8b0d3b9a9","tid":2013564,"uid":245409,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:20:36.000Z","msg":"點解要叫天津天海？係咪歧視天津人？<br />\n<br />\n應該叫新型天海"},{"pid":"2884bf07916d80e1863401ebcb3874ec6e115654","tid":2013564,"uid":13106,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"一代亞冠神隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1be25faa1e2d348cd8e4cf38c2d3222b2919f37","tid":2013564,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"咁就收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e573a11c5df98d83ef8a46661d642d